methods.make:
Creates a new DisplayWrapper around an Object. Returns null if the Object is null.

:param objectToWrap: (java.lang.Object) - the Object to wrap
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.preview.DisplayWrapper) a new DisplayWrapper, null if the Object is null

text:
Wraps Objects that cannot be displayed (e.g. not serializable or an unknown class) and allows them to be displayed as
 a String.
